<br>
I understand that this would be a significant revision to the way styles function, but if we're looking at a serious Style Review and looking at it from scratch, then I think it bears thinking about.<br>
<br>
If the Heavy Tank has Guard on the casters with a Light Tank standing beside him and that caster gets charged by an enemy, that Heavy Tank should be able to stun the attacker off the Guard (Guard functions as a Block in triggering Block-based styles, many of which are accompanied by medium- to long-duration stuns) while the Light Tank goes to town with a Block chain triggered by the Heavy Tank's block.<br>
<br>
I think this vision best exemplifies what I believe Mythic is shooting for in the new RvR experience.  It would alter the dynamic of RvR to focus a Heavy Tank's role more toward defense.  It would encourage Light Tanks to work together with Heavy Tanks for significant gains in efficiency and overall RvR survivability.<br>
<br>
It would also have the ancillary benefit that Scouts would be strongly desired in RvR groups as they are the single best blockers and guarders in the entire game (Guard 3 plus Dex as a Primary stat plus speccable shield).  <br>
<br>
Something to think about, anyway. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showMessageRange?topicID=351.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=351.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=351.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=351.topic&index=24><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=351.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.threadControl?topicID=351.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=351.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=351.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http:/